Technology Brief -- Storage Technology Corp.:
   Firm Posts Flat Earnings
   For Fiscal Fourth Quarter
For the year, Storage Technology said its profit grew less
than 1% to $93.1 million, or $2.33 a share, compared with
$92.4 million, or $2.64 a share, the year earlier. The 1990
results included a $1.3 million charge for retirement of
debt. Storage Technology had weighted average shares
outstanding of almost 40 million for 1991, compared with 35
million for 1990.
   Revenue for 1991 was $1.58 billion, up 2.6% from $1.55
billion in 1990.